<div class="row">
<div class="sixcol align-right last"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uZDmcrqI_sw?rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img alt="Play the video" class="canvas" src="/Templates/images/16x9-play-button.png" style="background-image: url('images/male-student-video-poster.jpg');"/></a></div>
<div class="sixcol">
<h2>Tour our beautiful campus with a current student.</h2>
<p>See what Samford is like through a current student&#8217;s eyes, and see new renovations of the Beeson University Center, including the Samford Shop and food court, all part of our commitment to exceptional learning.</p>
<p class="double-space"><a class="button" href="/admission/visit" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Schedule Your Visit</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
                                                                                <div class="blue-box content-box">
<div class="row">
<div class="sixcol"><img alt="Two female students conversing" class="canvas" src="/Templates/images/3x2-canvas.png" style="background-image: url('/admission/undergraduate/experience/images/Two-Female-Students-Conversing.jpg');"/></div>
<div class="sixcol last">
<h2>Connect <em>with</em> Samford</h2>
<blockquote>Connect with our inspiring campus today.</blockquote>
<p>Tour our timeless campus guided by current Samford students, or take your pick of a number of virtual options. Our goal is to connect you with an experience that works best for you. This visit is yours from start to finish. By the time it ends, you&#8217;ll know the truth: Your Samford life is just beginning.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
                                                                                <div class="content-box">
<div class="row">
<div class="fourcol">
<p><img alt="Samford Students Engaged in Classroom" height="335" src="/admission/undergraduate/experience/images/Samford-Students-Engaged-in-Classroom.jpg" width="485"/></p>
<h2>Powerful Learning</h2>
<p>Meeting online with our professors gives you a taste of a field that can spark your passions and launch your career. Learn how Samford opens career possibilities.</p>
<p class="double-space"><a class="button" href="/admission/undergraduate/experience/powerful-learning" title="Learn more about powerful learning at Samford.">Learn More</a></p>
