<h2>Caring Community</h2>
<p>Getting to know students on your visit places you in the center of our extraordinary warmhearted community. See how Samford nurtures bonds that last.</p>
<p class="double-space"><a class="button" href="/admission/undergraduate/experience/caring-community" title="Get started with a caring community at Samford.">Get Started</a></p>
