<p><img alt="Birmingham City Skyline" height="335" src="/admission/undergraduate/experience/images/Birmingham-Skyline.jpg" width="485"/></p>
<h2>Flourishing City</h2>
<p>Exploring Birmingham on your visit reveals rich opportunities for internships and careers and abundant places to discover the arts, great food, shopping and natural beauty. See how Samford makes the most of its city.</p>
<p class="double-space"><a class="button" href="/admission/undergraduate/experience/flourishing-city">Explore<span class="desktop"> Birmingham</span></a></p>
